Achievements.Name: You Swine

Achievements.Name: Bad Doggy
Achievements.Description: Rescue Trip from the Dog in less than 36 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Got the Horn
Achievements.Description: Rescue Trip from the Rhino in less than 35 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Mined the Gap

Achievements.Description: Kill a Broadcaster with 1 second on the clock.

Achievements.Name: Kebabed

Achievements.Name: Attacks Evasion
Achievements.Description: Perform 20 Evade Attacks that hit an enemy.

Achievements.Name: Tech Collector
Achievements.Description: Collect half of the Tech Orbs.
